{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484010/extras/Limited_Lives_EN.gif?t=1739698251\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484010/extras/LivesConsole.gif?t=1739698251\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every time you die, your body is recreated through cloning, but that's only half the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your memories are just as important. They are stored as data on a chip,  drilled deep into your brain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Without a chip, you\u2019re a hollow shell; an empty meat suit, lifeless and mindless.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And once they run out, it\u2019s <strong>GAME OVER</strong>. Your story is erased from existence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484010/extras/BrainChipExtraction.gif?t=1739698251\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The only way to reclaim brain chips is to find injectors capable of penetrating the skull and extracting a chip from your dead body. Isn\u2019t the cycle of life marvelous?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But be careful - everything comes at a price\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484010/extras/Save_Title_En_.gif?t=1739698251\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484010/extras/SaveGameCropped.gif?t=1739698251\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Save at the comfort of your safe room, or the game will save for you when you <strong>die</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But Remember: you have a limited amount of lives!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484010/extras/Keep_Lose_EN.gif?t=1739698251\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484010/extras/InventoryCropped.gif?t=1739698251\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Carry items in your inventory or store them in the convenience of your safe room. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you die, you can retrieve your items from your dead body - no time limits, no penalties. But remember: every death brings you closer to game over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484010/extras/WhatIsReal_EN.gif?t=1739698251\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484010/extras/RealFake.gif?t=1739698251\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484010/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739698251","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484010/page.bg.jpg?t=1739698251","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484010/f65b9dbcb2f07b6931f9068a0f87368c033665b0/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739698251","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484010/f65b9dbcb2f07b6931f9068a0f87368c033665b0/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739698251","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Immortum contains themes and imagery related to death that may be unsettling for some players. Viewer discretion is advised."},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484010/extras/L